translation: Vá para o Templo dos Mares.{#Name="Explanation"}
source: Make your way toward the Shrine of Seas.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Aaaah! Ela vai me matar!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Ah! Aaaah! She's gonna get me!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Não podemos deixá-la enconstar na Five!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: We won't let her lay a finger on Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Eu queria poder encostar nela...{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: I'd like to lay somethin' on Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Que diabos? Tá crescendo uma flor no olho dela!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: What the hell? An eye socket is no place to be growin' a flower!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: She gets points for originality...{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: She gets points for originality...{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: A guerra chegou até aqui...{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: So war has come to the Land of Seas...{#Name="Soldier F"}
Try not to piss yourself, kid!{#Name="Soldier B"}
If we fight bravely, we might get an audience with Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier C"}
Ooh! And then we'll get to see them beautiful gams!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Impeçam-na, não importa o que custe!
source: She's after our Intoner! Stop her, no matter what!{#Name="Soldier A"}
Where are the damn reinforcements!?{#Name="Soldier E"}
The d-dragon... The dragon is...{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Desde quando dragões se importam com gente!?
source: I thought dragons didn't care about people! What's going on!?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Ela está controlando-o de alguma forma...
source: She's somehow able to control that dragon...{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Erga essa espada, idiota! Você quer morrer?
source: Keep your sword up, fool! You want to die?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Eu não consigo! Estou com medo!
E você acha que nós não estamos!?
source: You think the rest of us are ENJOYING this!?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Ela está com Dito! Ela está segura!
source: She's with Dito! She's safe!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Por que ela gosta daquele garoto idiota?
source: Bah! Why does she waste time with that pathetic kid?{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Vamos sacrificar nossas vidas pela nossa Intoner!
source: Our lives are sacrifice to our mighty Intoner!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Eu só queria... Estar... Com a Five...
source: Just once...before I died...I wanted to be with Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier B"}
We can't hold her! We need support!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Ela é tão veloz com a lâmina...
source: Her blade is so fast...{#Name="Soldier E"}
Is it skill? Or something else?{#Name="Soldier F"}
Get away! Get away from me!{#Name="Soldier G"}
We can't make contact with any of our allies...{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Se isso continuar, vamos pra debaixo de um caixão!
source: If this keeps up, we're all gonna be worm food!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Tem tanta gente em todo lugar!
source: Wow, look at all of them! They're everywhere!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Esmague-os como as formigas que são.
source: They're like ants to you. Just crush 'em.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Nossa, olha a água! É tão bonita!
source: Wow, look at the water here! It's so pretty!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Afunda logo esse maldito navio, vai.
source: Just sink the goddamn battleship, will you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Não acho que posso quebrar essa barricada.
source: I don't think I can break this barricade.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Parece que eu vou ter que subir{LF}e dar a volta de algum jeito.
source: Guess I'll just have to climb up and go{LF}around somehow.{#Name="Zero"}
Heh. That's a pretty half-assed way to{LF}try and slow me down...{#Name="Zero"}
So...what kind of sister is Five?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Resumindo, ela só pensa em coisas sujas.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It means all she thinks about is dirty stuff.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ah. Então ela é como você!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh. So she's just like you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Dá pra você calar a boca?{#Name="Zero"}
Parece que as pessoas viviam por aqui.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Looks like people used to live here at some point.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Deve ser legal viver perto do mar.{LF}Imagina o tanto de peixe gostoso!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Must be nice living near the sea.{LF}Think of all the yummy fish!{#Name="Mikhail"}
What the hell? Where's the shrine?{#Name="Zero"}
Dammit. I think we've been had.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Mas, não precisamos lutar e tudo ficou bem{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: だって、戦わなくてもよくなったもん{#Name="ミハイル"}
Heh. What are you looking at, shithead?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Que piada. Por que todos os grandões{LF}são lentos e idiotas?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Heh. Look at this. Why are big guys{LF}so slow and stupid?{#Name="Zero"}
You don't have to say it twice!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Você é grande, mas não é dois.{LF}Você já era.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Whatever it is, if it gets in my way,{LF}it's going down.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Cuidado, Zero! Esse cara é forte!{LF}Muito forte!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Just be careful, Zero! This guy's strong!{LF}Super strong!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Pffft. Ela acha que vai me parar com isso?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Pfft. She thinks that'll be enough to stop me?{#Name="Zero"}
Heh. They're really rolling out the red carpet.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Me mostre do que você é capaz, Five.{#Name="Zero"}
source: All right, Five. Let's see what you've got.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: O que vai acontecer quando você matar as suas irmãs?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: So...what happens once you kill all your sisters?{#Name="Mikhail"}
Oh...uh... Ha ha! I totally believed you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Quando eu matá-las, vou poder usar seus poderes.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Once I kill them, I can exploit their powers.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Então você quer roubar{LF}a magia delas?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: So you're going steal their Intoner magic{LF}and stuff?{#Name="Mikhail"}
